claim: Time Lords do not prevent time from being subverted or abused.
premise_source_doc_sentence: They developed a culture of custodianship and time-related technologies based on this perception which includes strictly controlled space/time travel machines  (  known as `` TARDISes ''  )  and monitoring devices to travel through time and to prevent time from being subverted or abused -- although actual action was described as rare in practice due to their traditional policy of strict non-interference and neutrality .
